OL,3,COne person dead and child in hospital
OL,4,Cafter train hits car on level crossing
OL,6,FA person has died and a child is
OL,7,Ffighting for their life following a
OL,8,Fcollision between a train and a car on
OL,9,Fa level crossing.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FStation Road, Hoghton, near Preston at
OL,13,F8.50am on 25 June following reports of
OL,14,Fthe crash.
OL,16,FFire and ambulance crews attended
OL,17,Falong with officers from British
OL,18,FTransport Police and Lancashire Police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
