PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782472699
OL,3,COne person dead and child in hospital
OL,4,Cafter train hits car on level crossing
OL,6,FThe child has been taken to Alder Hey
OL,7,FHospital, and no passengers on the
OL,8,Ftrain required medical treatment,
OL,9,FNorth West Ambulance Service (NWAS)
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FA NWAS spokesperson said: "We
OL,13,Fresponded to an incident in the
OL,14,FHoghton area of Lancashire after
OL,15,Freports of a collision between a train
OL,16,Fand a car at 8.50am today (25 June).
OL,18,F"Several clinical teams attended the
OL,19,Fscene, including our hazardous area
OL,20,Fresponse team and two air ambulances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782472699
OL,3,COne person dead and child in hospital
OL,4,Cafter train hits car on level crossing
OL,6,F"Sadly, a child has sustained life
OL,7,Fthreatening injuries and has been
OL,8,Ftaken to Alder Hey Children's Hospital
OL,9,Ffor further treatment.
OL,11,F"No passengers travelling on the train
OL,12,Frequired treatment from ambulance
OL,13,Fcrews."
OL,15,FLancashire Police confirmed officers
OL,16,Fare assisting at the scene and have
OL,17,Fadvised motorists to avoid the area.
OL,19,FAn investigation is underway to
OL,20,Festablish the circumstances
OL,21,Fsurrounding the collision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
