PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782472699
OL,3,COne person dead and child in hospital
OL,4,Cafter train hits car on level crossing
OL,6,FA BTP spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fcurrently on scene at a level crossing
OL,8,Fin Hoghton, Lancashire, following
OL,9,Freports that a train had struck a car.
OL,11,F"Paramedics and the fire service are
OL,12,Falso in attendance. Two people were in
OL,13,Fthe car and sadly one was pronounced
OL,14,Fdead the scene, the other is being
OL,15,Ftaken to hospital with life-
OL,16,Fthreatening injuries.
OL,18,F"There have been no other injuries
OL,19,Freported from passengers on the train
OL,20,Fat this time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
