OL,3,COne person dead and child in hospital
OL,4,Cafter train hits car on level crossing
OL,6,FAny witnesses are asked to text 61016
OL,7,Fquoting reference 152 of 25 June.
OL,9,FThis is a breaking story. More
OL,10,Finformation to follow.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
